 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the designer##3
 8. the person driving the subway is the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking juice##1
11. the writer is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

