The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, van
 1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking fanta##2
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person watching musical movies and the person driving the van##2
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
11. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
12. the person who growslily is the person eating peach##1

